    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Above 18 years, Meeting the central obesity criteria Cases where colonoscopy is
             performed under elective conditions

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  In case of emergency, The process is terminated due to bad bowel preparation,
             Inflammatory bowel disease, Serious arrhythmia, Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease
             Coronary artery disease The previous abdominal surgery
